    <item>
      <title>贸易商付出更多痛苦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的盛大贸易关税将击败美国经济，因此彭博社的货币量最高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500下沉4％，因为关税冲击马刺债券集会：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争的影响周四遍布全球市场，击落股票并促进了进入固定收益避风港的飞行。美国股票和美元对猜测最糟糕的卖出总统的贸易攻势将阻碍美国经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当美国贸易战争颠覆全球前景时，市场抛售会加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贸易越来越深，唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战将加剧了美国的损失将颠覆全球经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
